OL,3,CTwo people in hospital after alleged
OL,4,Cassault with knife and plank of wood
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for information
OL,7,Fafter a man and woman were allegedly
OL,8,Fassaulted in Cardiff.
OL,10,FIt is believed the woman was attacked
OL,11,Fwith a knife while the man was hit
OL,12,Fwith a plank of wood.
OL,14,FBoth have been taken to hospital to
OL,15,Freceive treatment.
OL,17,FThe incident occurred in the Llanishen
OL,18,Farea of Cardiff, at around lunchtime
OL,19,Fon Sunday , 21 June.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
