OL,3,CTwo people in hospital after alleged
OL,4,Cassault with knife and plank of wood
OL,6,FA 37-year old man from Splott has been
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of affray,
OL,8,Fpossession of an offensive weapon, and
OL,9,Fdrink driving.
OL,11,FPolice had been called to the area
OL,12,Fafter reports of "a man chasing a
OL,13,Fwoman" through residential streets.
OL,15,FA spokesperson from South Wales Police
OL,16,Fconfirmed they were called to
OL,17,FTempleton Avenue, Llanishen, at
OL,18,F12:15pm following 'a report of a man
OL,19,Fchasing a woman.'
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
