OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1782118104
OL,3,CTwo people in hospital after alleged
OL,4,Cassault with knife and plank of wood
OL,6,FThey continued: "Officers attended
OL,7,Fpromptly and found that both a man and
OL,8,Fa woman had been assaulted. Both were
OL,9,Ftaken to hospital for further
OL,10,Ftreatment.
OL,12,F"At this stage, it is believed the
OL,13,Fwoman was assaulted with a knife, and
OL,14,Fthe man was assaulted with a plank of
OL,15,Fwood."
OL,17,FThey added: "A 37-year-old man from
OL,18,FSplott, Cardiff, has been arrested on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of affray, possession of an
OL,20,Foffensive weapon, and drink driving."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
