OL,3,CTwo people in hospital after alleged
OL,4,Cassault with knife and plank of wood
OL,6,FSouth Wales Police detective inspector
OL,7,FSarah Lee said it was believed that
OL,8,Fthe parties involved in the incident
OL,9,Fwere known to each other.
OL,11,FShe said: "We know that incidents of
OL,12,Fthis nature can be upsetting for the
OL,13,Flocal community, and we want to
OL,14,Freassure residents that we acted
OL,15,Fquickly to bring the situation under
OL,16,Fcontrol and support those involved.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
