OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1782118104
OL,3,CTwo people in hospital after alleged
OL,4,Cassault with knife and plank of wood
OL,6,F"Our officers are carrying out
OL,7,Fthorough enquiries to establish the
OL,8,Ffull circumstances, and a man remains
OL,9,Fin custody. We believe this was an
OL,10,Fisolated incident between three people
OL,11,Fknown to one another, and there is no
OL,12,Fwider threat."
OL,14,FSouth Wales Police are appealing to
OL,15,Fanyone with information or CCTV
OL,16,Ffootage to come forward.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/5
